  "detailed_description": "<i><strong>UNHEIM</strong> is an atmospheric horror surveillance game set in Bavaria, Germany. As a self-proclaimed paranormal investigator, you are equipped with a mixture of various state-of-the-art surveillance tools and strangely outdated reporting devices. Be warned: the beings you observe are all too aware of your presence and don't always react kindly. Can you survive the night?</i><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/eb216e853a135e085b9fb07a4f33069b.poster.avif?t=1752580840\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/eb216e853a135e085b9fb07a4f33069b.webm?t=1752580840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/eb216e853a135e085b9fb07a4f33069b.mp4?t=1752580840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Direct Entity Interactions:</h2> Set apart from typical horror surveillance games, UNHEIM offers direct confrontations with its horrifying entities. Each encounter comes with unique patterns, behaviors, and means of interaction: outwit these beings to survive, or face a swift and terrifying end.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/5e4e95d89d81b6b1acb912f541d3f274.poster.avif?t=1752580840\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/5e4e95d89d81b6b1acb912f541d3f274.webm?t=1752580840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/5e4e95d89d81b6b1acb912f541d3f274.mp4?t=1752580840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Engaging Progression System:</h2> As you advance through the levels, your surveillance toolkit expands, enhancing your ability to detect and report paranormal events. This progression system adds depth to your journey, offering new challenges and tools as you delve deeper into UNHEIM.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/d980c32ccc095110019b108350ed726f.poster.avif?t=1752580840\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/d980c32ccc095110019b108350ed726f.webm?t=1752580840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/d980c32ccc095110019b108350ed726f.mp4?t=1752580840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Superior Audio-Visual Immersion:</h2> Dive into an experience marked by unparalleled audio and visual quality. Every element contributes to the creation of a hauntingly beautiful and terrifying atmosphere.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/a83d9de84b7f3256d3e8e5835795e81d.poster.avif?t=1752580840\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/a83d9de84b7f3256d3e8e5835795e81d.webm?t=1752580840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/a83d9de84b7f3256d3e8e5835795e81d.mp4?t=1752580840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ruthless Challenge:</h2> UNHEIM offers a uniquely demanding experience and is exceptionally difficult to master. It's crafted for those who seek an extraordinarily intense test of their memory, observation and resilience skills. Are you prepared for an unforgiving test of your observation skills and stress resistance?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/768f2590fb30ca52c4f0a20e24aebb9d.poster.avif?t=1752580840\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/768f2590fb30ca52c4f0a20e24aebb9d.webm?t=1752580840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/768f2590fb30ca52c4f0a20e24aebb9d.mp4?t=1752580840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unpredictable Gameplay and Replayability:</h2> Thanks to randomized elements and the variety of challenges in several levels, UNHEIM guarantees a relentless and unpredictable experience each time you play, ensuring that no two playthroughs are alike.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/dd1700c5c46636e8989d581f5012ce07.poster.avif?t=1752580840\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/dd1700c5c46636e8989d581f5012ce07.webm?t=1752580840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/dd1700c5c46636e8989d581f5012ce07.mp4?t=1752580840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Twitch Integration:</h2> Stream viewers can actively participate by voting up camera IDs where they suspect paranormal activity or changes, creating a collaborative and engaging experience for both the streamer and the audience.",
  "about_the_game": "<i><strong>UNHEIM</strong> is an atmospheric horror surveillance game set in Bavaria, Germany. As a self-proclaimed paranormal investigator, you are equipped with a mixture of various state-of-the-art surveillance tools and strangely outdated reporting devices. Be warned: the beings you observe are all too aware of your presence and don't always react kindly. Can you survive the night?</i><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/eb216e853a135e085b9fb07a4f33069b.poster.avif?t=1752580840\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/eb216e853a135e085b9fb07a4f33069b.webm?t=1752580840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/eb216e853a135e085b9fb07a4f33069b.mp4?t=1752580840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Direct Entity Interactions:</h2> Set apart from typical horror surveillance games, UNHEIM offers direct confrontations with its horrifying entities. Each encounter comes with unique patterns, behaviors, and means of interaction: outwit these beings to survive, or face a swift and terrifying end.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/5e4e95d89d81b6b1acb912f541d3f274.poster.avif?t=1752580840\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/5e4e95d89d81b6b1acb912f541d3f274.webm?t=1752580840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686110/extras/5e4e95d89d81b6b1acb912f541d3f274.mp4?t=1752580840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\